{"tid":676391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"袁嘉蔚田灣女孩攻區選","createTime":"2018-05-24T10:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T04:42:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac7f0094f51714afeabeba92f27da1fa22ca281","tid":676391,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:28:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180524/20399823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F20399823&d=vS6jpcaqlwLAjihyyT9lsYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=559a8386\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F20399823&h=7734e216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180524/20399823</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月24日 <br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：袁嘉蔚田灣女孩攻區選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180524/large/a09a04a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180524%2Flarge%2Fa09a04a.gif&h=f8ac19e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■袁嘉蔚近日變身「田灣女孩」，似乎備戰區選之意滿滿。袁嘉蔚fb圖片<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n呢排社運界多咗個「田灣女孩」，事事以田灣出發嘅人原來係早前突然退出香港眾志嘅袁嘉蔚（Tiffany），佢最近開咗個人專頁，仲發表題為〈田灣不應該如此〉嘅文章，獲眾志前黨友黃之鋒同羅冠聰等人share，更落hashtag「田灣女孩」，其中之鋒除咗喺留言同畀心心，再hashtag埋「心蔚田灣，撐田灣女孩」，仲搞笑咁採納網民建議，話袁嘉蔚日後開地辦，可以叫做「蔚袁堂」！<br />\n<br />\n咦，有傳Tiffany會戰明年區選，似乎出戰之意，相當明顯！<br />\n<br />\nTiffany指近萬人居住嘅田灣邨，商場只剩便利店同提款機，田灣外更有條長命斜，令老弱傷殘甚至成年人由山腳走到屋邨亦相當辛苦，原因係領展入主後商場冇民生商舖，連升降機早排都被停止服務，形容呢個係「領展的惡果」。<br />\n<br />\n佢繼而解構呢個領展惡果係源於社區錯誤規劃，呼籲田灣居民同佢一齊爭取安居同宜居嘅家，咁擔任當區議員，又確實係爭取社區變得更好嘅好方法，而現時呢區區議員、建制派陳富明，上屆係自動當選喎，唔知準備好要競選未？  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：馬丁囝囝　6.2小登科 (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (馬龍)"},{"pid":"14137daea9d9e9688b5736f07d9c5c8786260990","tid":676391,"uid":57376,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"田灣人俾支那遊客輪姦左幾年都唔識反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5509250ffb952cd2e47e3df737e70dd655dfb19e","tid":676391,"uid":35699,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:50:16.000Z","msg":"田灣臭西"},{"pid":"51e071bb38b49136851820c41d90bbb7923c1e1c","tid":676391,"uid":133680,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T11:48:37.000Z","msg":"唔怪得前排仇阿達又話無講過粗口罵佢係誤會又幫佢講說話，原來又想黏人。留名等睇佢遲d又是其是非其非黏袁嘉蔚屌黃毓民佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4867347076b7019a986e07e9f17cedd99cd6a94d","tid":676391,"uid":123524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51e071bb38b49136851820c41d90bbb7923c1e1c","tid":676391,"uid":133680,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T11:48:37.000Z","msg":"唔怪得前排仇阿達又話無講過粗口罵佢係誤會又幫佢講說話，原來又想黏人。留名等睇佢遲d又是其是非其非黏袁嘉蔚屌黃毓民佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T23:45:22.000Z","msg":"昏迷左四個月<br />\n仇思達食到佢味？"},{"pid":"4756ec81cde821b8bf73a8a2b096d415c24f2ef3","tid":676391,"uid":61546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14137daea9d9e9688b5736f07d9c5c8786260990","tid":676391,"uid":57376,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"田灣人俾支那遊客輪姦左幾年都唔識反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T00:13:52.000Z","msg":"陳富明上屆係自動當選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb2577bb9f85ec96066de3ac379c84d1ff3abc4","tid":676391,"uid":44810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14137daea9d9e9688b5736f07d9c5c8786260990","tid":676391,"uid":57376,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"田灣人俾支那遊客輪姦左幾年都